Reasoning: The paper discusses the use of data from online sharing systems to extract relationships between users and create a multidimensional social network. This involves topics related to social media, social networks, and information retrieval, which are covered by the sub-categories of cs.SI (Social and Information Networks), cs.SD (Software Engineering), and cs.IR (Information Retrieval). The paper also discusses the creation of a social recommender system, which involves topics related to human-computer interaction (cs.HC) and multimedia (cs.MM).
